"Counter Strike : Source content for those who don't have it"

----------------------------------------

This ZIP files came with this text file and a folder called "CSS Content Addon
(Jul2014)". This is the folder you will use in the instructions below.

----------------------------------------

NOW FOR THE INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS!

- Go to your Garry's Mod folder where the game is installed:
C:Program Files (x86)SteamSteamAppscommonGarrysModgarrysmodaddons

Make sure you are inside the "addons" folder.

- Extract "CSS Content Addon (Jul2014)" into the "addons" folder.

- Restart Garry's Mod if it's currently running.

- Done.
